<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA12d184n10-ptr" id="PJA12d184n10">10</a>
<p> From this statement is derived the phrase militia diplomacy and all that the term implies. It is doubtful, however, that in 1782 <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr> considered himself less skilled, knowledgeable, or prepared than his European counterparts.</p>
